               <p>JOHN ROGERS. I live at <placeName id="t18200112-106-crimeloc602">Old Brentford</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18200112-106-crimeloc602" type="placeName" value="Old Brentford"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18200112-106-crimeloc602" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200112-106-off600 t18200112-106-crimeloc602"></join> - the prisoner lodged at my house, and paid 2 s. a week. He had a bed to himself, On the 6th of December I missed a blanket and sheet off his bed; I asked him about them, he said they were there when he came down. Next morning I missed the books; I then took him to Mr. Lees, where I found the books; Lees said he bought them of him, The prisoner then said he pledged the blanket and sheet at Nicholls's, and said I should find the duplicate in his bedroom drawer, which I did.</p>
               <p>
